
Purchase Ticket:
1.
POST /api/train/purchase
{
  "firstName": "michael",
  "lastName": "scott",
  "email": "michael.scott@example.com"
}
2. View receipt 
get -  /api/train/receipt?email=michael.scott@example.com
3.View Users by section 
get -  /api/train/users?section=A
4. Remove user from train
delete -  /api/train/remove?email=jim.carrey@example.com
5. Modify user's seat
put - /api/train/modify?email=michael.scott@example.com&newSection=B